<quantity box="[818,904,295,322]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.7" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" unit="mm" value="9.7">9.7 mm</quantity>
to ovipositor tip.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="34.[151,1293,259,394]" box="[199,1285,331,358]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">Protibia row PD with numerous macrosetae, 20 or more. Metatarsomere I with 4 apical platellae.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="34.[151,1293,259,394]" box="[199,549,367,394]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,272,367,393]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">Color.</emphasis>
